data.description: Welcome to 650 Capon St, in Strasburg, VA, where opportunity knocks for investors and house flippers alike!  Presenting an exciting prospect for those seeking a property ripe for renovation.    Built in 1945, this property offers a glimpse into a cherished era of architectural design and craftsmanship.  Nestled on a generous 1/4 acre lot, this residence boasts a tranquil setting, perfect for creating your dream home.  The homeowner has already begun renovations on the property showing off what the possibilities are with this property!  With a total of 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, this property provides an excellent foundation for customization and personalization.  Whether you envision a modern open-concept layout, or prefer to honor the home's historic charm, the canvas is yours to create.  Calling on the expertise of architects, designers, and skilled tradespeople, you have the opportunity to restore this home to its former glory while infusing it with contemporary finishes and amenities.  Imagine the satisfaction of transforming this house into a showcase of design ingenuity.  For investors and house flippers, this property presents an excellent opportunity to add value and maximize their return on investment.  Your efforts and vision will surely be rewarded.  Dont' miss your chance to be a part of the revitalization of this property.  Take the reins and bring your ideas to life!
